[socisth agnih]{To such}तं {you,}त्वा॑ {O most brilliant,}शोचिष्ठ {shining bright!}दीदिवः।
[sumnm]{For favour}सु॒म्नाय॑ [kalh]{now}नू॒न [pryanm]{(we) come}मी॑महे॒ [skayh agnih]{for friends.}सखि॑भ्यः।
